{"tid":1999221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(警世) 香港冇\"記者註册\", 所謂記者證只係職公司員證","createTime":"2020-05-03T04:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T06:10:59.000Z","uid":34514,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1d89dc4412ac873d12033d4e1fbfa3a9c05a7e","tid":1999221,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"香港嘅記者證只係由傳媒公司俾嘅&quot;職員證&quot;, 唔係乜嘢正式資格.<br />\n依家全香港就只有差佬同港共先會想限制記者採訪, 所以先不斷同你講&quot;要有記者證先可以採訪&quot;, &quot;香港有假記者&quot;, 最終憑空創作一個&quot;記者認證&quot;出嚟.<br />\n<br />\n以下係for 五毛:<br />\n呢個係特區政府嘅聲明:<br />\n<br />\n政府澄清發放記者證事宜<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n     就有網上消息指一個名為「香港新聞傳媒管理中心」於二○一三年二月十九日開始發出香港新聞記者證和香港新聞工作者證，政府發言人今日（九月二十七日）回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n     香港沒有官方機構統一發放記者證。獲邀出席政府公開採訪活動的傳媒代表須出示其所屬機構發出的記者證，如有疑問，政府官員會直接致電其所屬傳媒機構，以核實其身分。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月27日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間18時43分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/27/P2019092700734.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F27%2FP2019092700734.htm&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjggoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=050a4c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/27/P2019092700734.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f6ae493eb49d6d514c0b26c8bb97eb0665af46a3","tid":1999221,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"78ca08123d68fab2e08bc13c353aee5563779e3a","tid":1999221,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54e069dcce93a13e91a52111f2e6c4f408e94d3a","tid":1999221,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6400c557bf262fc7ea3d0bcd5475825eab6cb840","tid":1999221,"uid":199012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"8b781e8ae564a998124abc86866e2ebec6135fa1","tid":1999221,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f651dec5e03dd711145a796f287ae32b27f0faf4","tid":1999221,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d594518b63651d8867d3e2b2a055ffebf99462ff","tid":1999221,"uid":231583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公民記者概念出現咗好多年，港共想倒退番去秦漢時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全民都可以係記者，無人會係假記者</span></span>"},{"pid":"d8d099d4cf68cabe6536389e84aee9f19532baec","tid":1999221,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"唔係記協咩"},{"pid":"d2c63c6843bfd882bc3ef6e3ad36c0ee9053b133","tid":1999221,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d594518b63651d8867d3e2b2a055ffebf99462ff","tid":1999221,"uid":231583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公民記者概念出現咗好多年，港共想倒退番去秦漢時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全民都可以係記者，無人會係假記者</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"Exactly! <br />\n順便推!"},{"pid":"2f3b5f97c7d66e39ebd17fd9b24b2d47d20ce311","tid":1999221,"uid":34514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8d099d4cf68cabe6536389e84aee9f19532baec","tid":1999221,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"唔係記協咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"記協唔同會計師公會/工程師學會嗰啲認證組織嚟"},{"pid":"b459e45e0bcbe59f11d63deb7659767c9a009c73","tid":1999221,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"